  <body region="amara-subtitle-area">
    <div>
      <p begin="00:00:13,667" end="00:00:34,233">[clicking]</p>
      <p begin="00:00:35,133" end="00:00:36,541">&#65279;[plane landing]</p>
      <p begin="00:00:37,333" end="00:00:39,833">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">- [Tiffany] I was flying to New York to visit this good friend of mine,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:00:40,067" end="00:00:42,641">and just as the plane was landing<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>I was getting that kind of, you know</p>
      <p begin="00:00:42,641" end="00:00:45,926">fidgety feeling of wanting to check <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>my cellphone and I was thinking,</p>
      <p begin="00:00:45,926" end="00:00:48,035">it wasn't that long ago<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>that when a plane landed</p>
      <p begin="00:00:48,035" end="00:00:49,861">we would have lunged<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>for our cigarette packs.</p>
      <p begin="00:00:50,034" end="00:00:52,600">Well, actually we used to all <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>smoke on the planes.</p>
      <p begin="00:00:52,967" end="00:00:54,672">[Laughter]</p>
      <p begin="00:00:54,672" end="00:00:56,808">But nowadays when a plane lands, <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>we all lunge for our cellphones</p>
      <p begin="00:00:56,808" end="00:00:59,204">that same kind of addictive fever</p>
      <p begin="00:00:59,204" end="00:01:02,296">like we can't stand not being connected <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>for a second longer.</p>
      <p begin="00:01:02,296" end="00:01:03,519">And it doesn't let up.</p>
      <p begin="00:01:03,519" end="00:01:06,447">Walking down the street in Manhattan<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>no one is making an eye contact.</p>
      <p begin="00:01:06,447" end="00:01:09,159">Everybody is looking down,<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>they're texting, they're tweeting.</p>
      <p begin="00:01:09,159" end="00:01:10,998">I half expected to see <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>the Statue of Liberty,</p>
      <p begin="00:01:10,998" end="00:01:14,283">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">torch with one hand, texting with the other.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:01:14,283" end="00:01:16,734">So I'm finally at lunch with this <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>really good friend of mine,</p>
      <p begin="00:01:16,734" end="00:01:18,909">and we're having a fantastic time --<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>I haven't seen her in years --</p>
      <p begin="00:01:18,909" end="00:01:20,874">laughing, drinking, talking,</p>
      <p begin="00:01:20,874" end="00:01:23,996">but I'm still getting this urge <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>to check my email.</p>
      <p begin="00:01:23,996" end="00:01:26,442">I was like, Tiffany stay focused, <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>you traveled all the way</p>
      <p begin="00:01:26,442" end="00:01:28,821">across the United States <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>to see her, stay focused.</p>
      <p begin="00:01:28,821" end="00:01:31,578">But eventually it was like <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>it overtook me.</p>
      <p begin="00:01:31,578" end="00:01:34,183">And then I faked needing<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>to go to the bathroom.</p>
      <p begin="00:01:34,183" end="00:01:39,413">So I excused myself, grabbed my phone,<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>go into the bathroom stall,</p>
      <p begin="00:01:39,413" end="00:01:44,152">kind of hiding, texting, emailing, <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>thinking, "What have I become?"</p>
      <p begin="00:01:44,152" end="00:02:29,698">&#9834; [lively music] &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:02:29,698" end="00:02:33,874">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">- Technology is clearly changing usand the way we connect with our friends</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:02:33,874" end="00:02:38,403">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">our families and the world around us.So I set out to make a film about,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:02:38,403" end="00:02:42,387">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">what it means to be connected in the 21st century.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:02:42,387" end="00:02:45,435">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">For 200,000 years we've been connecting through networks</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:02:45,435" end="00:02:49,257">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">both natural and technological.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:02:49,257" end="00:02:51,283">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Today our networks have expanded to a point</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:02:51,283" end="00:02:55,777">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">where the've given the world a central nervous system.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:02:55,777" end="00:02:59,180">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Something happens in one placeand we can see it, feel it</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:02:59,180" end="00:03:02,732">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">and do something about it,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:03:02,732" end="00:03:05,917">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">which has such huge potential.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:03:05,917" end="00:03:07,128">[splash]</p>
      <p begin="00:03:07,128" end="00:03:10,991">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">But technology has also ledto the biggest problems of our day.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:03:10,991" end="00:03:13,191">[sewing machines rattling]</p>
      <p begin="00:03:13,191" end="00:03:16,615">[machine gun firing]</p>
      <p begin="00:03:16,615" end="00:03:20,184">[crashing]</p>
      <p begin="00:03:20,184" end="00:03:26,040">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">It's accelerating our connectednessin ways we can't even predict.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:03:26,040" end="00:03:29,161">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Take the honeybees,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:03:29,161" end="00:03:31,161">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">their recent disappearanceis the perfect example</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:03:31,161" end="00:03:34,844">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">of how everything is connected.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:03:34,844" end="00:03:38,345">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Albert Einstein predicted that ifhoneybees were to disappear completely,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:03:38,345" end="00:03:42,638">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">humanity would be gone in four years.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:03:42,638" end="00:03:47,098">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">No more honeybees, no more food being pollinated,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:03:47,098" end="00:03:51,292">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">no more humans.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:03:51,292" end="00:03:53,789">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">So if one change in our over-connected world</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:03:53,789" end="00:03:56,676">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">can have such far-reaching consequences,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:03:56,676" end="00:03:59,038">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">how do we use the power of all these connections</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:03:59,038" end="00:04:03,518">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">to turn things around?</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:04:03,518" end="00:04:07,436">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">This was the kind of question I was exploring in this film.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:04:07,436" end="00:04:10,345">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">And then I had this yearthat turned my world upside down.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:04:10,345" end="00:04:13,931">[siren wailing]</p>
      <p begin="00:04:13,931" end="00:04:16,415">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">And forced me to rethink everything I thought I understood</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:04:16,415" end="00:04:17,821">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">about the ways we're connected.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:04:17,821" end="00:04:21,815">[siren wailing]</p>
      <p begin="00:04:21,815" end="00:04:26,353">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Let me back up.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:04:26,353" end="00:04:30,531">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">When I was growing up,I had my own version of Einstein.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:04:30,531" end="00:04:33,764">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">I called him Dad.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:04:33,764" end="00:04:39,059">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">He was the one who taught me to look for connections in the first place.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:04:39,059" end="00:04:42,727">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">He was a general surgeonwith a special interest in the brain.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:04:42,727" end="00:04:49,879">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">And he always found entertaining waysto teach us about his work.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:04:49,879" end="00:04:52,488">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">When I was in third grade, he came to my class on career day</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:04:52,488" end="00:04:54,510">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">with a huge ice cream container.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:04:54,510" end="00:04:55,810">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">He put in on the teacher's desk</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:04:55,810" end="00:04:58,995">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">and he started talking about the human brain.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:04:58,995" end="00:05:01,729">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">He said the way the brain worksis very complicated.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:05:01,729" end="00:05:05,942">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">But a simple way to think about itis that it has two hemispheres.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:05:05,942" end="00:05:08,199">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">The left brain breaks things downand creates order,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:05:08,199" end="00:05:11,926">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">and the right brain recognizes patterns and processes emotions.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:05:11,926" end="00:05:13,667">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">And he talked about how the two hemispheres</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:05:13,667" end="00:05:16,445">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">have to work together.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:05:16,445" end="00:05:19,513">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">And then at the end of his lessonhe opened up the ice cream cartoon</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:05:19,513" end="00:05:22,869">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">and there was this real human brain in formaldehyde.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:05:22,869" end="00:05:26,071">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Everybody freaked out.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:05:26,071" end="00:05:30,454">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">And then he took us all out for ice cream.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:05:30,454" end="00:05:33,719">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">In addition to being a surgeon,my father also wrote best selling books,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:05:33,719" end="00:05:37,205">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">that he links between disparate fields.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:05:37,205" end="00:05:39,551">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">He searched for patterns throughout history to give insight</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:05:39,551" end="00:05:42,301">into why we do what we do.</p>
      <p begin="00:05:42,301" end="00:05:45,706">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">In this first book he drew parallels between breakthroughs in art,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:05:45,706" end="00:05:48,384">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">and breakthroughs in science.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:05:48,384" end="00:05:52,691">- And you know the artist expresses <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>the nature of reality</p>
      <p begin="00:05:52,691" end="00:05:54,733">using image and metaphor.</p>
      <p begin="00:05:54,733" end="00:05:58,354">And the physicist, he's investigating <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>the nature of reality</p>
      <p begin="00:05:58,354" end="00:06:01,193">and expresses it <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>using numbers and equations.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:01,193" end="00:06:04,083">But it's the same thing<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>they're just different languages.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:04,083" end="00:06:07,854">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">- Like how cubism challenged viewers' notions of space and time,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:06:07,854" end="00:06:12,231">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">right before Einstein publishedhis theories about space and time.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:06:14,133" end="00:06:16,333">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Or how the artist Zoroaster did painting</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:06:16,333" end="00:06:18,608">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">using tiny dotsright around the same time</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:06:18,608" end="00:06:22,619">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">that scientists theorized molecules.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:06:22,619" end="00:06:27,131">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">He found examples like these throughout history.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:06:27,131" end="00:06:35,575">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">His books influenced a lot of people.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:06:35,575" end="00:06:37,457">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Sometimes he was criticizedfor not being</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:06:37,457" end="00:06:39,825">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">an expert on the fields he wrote about.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:06:39,825" end="00:06:41,705">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">But I think it was his outsider perspective</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:06:41,705" end="00:06:47,396">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">that allowed him to see these bigger connections.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:06:47,396" end="00:06:50,915">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">My father could talk about any subject.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:06:50,915" end="00:06:55,053">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">We like to call him "Leonipedia".</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:06:55,053" end="00:06:58,592">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">He and I had been talking about makinga film together for years.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:06:58,592" end="00:07:01,230">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">So when I started researchingall these connections</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:07:01,230" end="00:07:04,256">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">and how we could use them to help solve our problems,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:07:04,256" end="00:07:08,138">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">it was natural to ask him to be one of the co-writers,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:07:08,138" end="00:07:13,430">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">especially since he and my mompretty much co-wrote my brain.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:07:13,430" end="00:07:18,179">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">And I definitely needed help --just look at my first notes.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:07:18,179" end="00:07:26,935">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">I spent weeks staring at this picture wondering where to even begin.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:07:26,935" end="00:07:29,504">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Everything is so intertwined</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:07:29,504" end="00:07:33,230">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">and I thought maybethat's part of the problem --</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:07:33,230" end="00:07:38,828">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">that we try to deal with all all of these issues in isolation.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:07:38,828" end="00:07:41,622">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Why did we start doing that?</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:07:41,622" end="00:07:45,019">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">So I turned to my father for some perspective.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:07:45,019" end="00:07:48,699">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">He said, go to the past and look for patterns.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:07:48,699" end="00:07:53,344">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Pretend you're an alien lookingat this unusual species called humans.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:07:53,344" end="00:07:56,347">&#9834;[humming] &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:07:56,347" end="00:07:57,205">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">So I did.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:07:57,205" end="00:07:58,229">[whirring of cameras]</p>
      <p begin="00:07:58,229" end="00:08:00,606">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">I hired a narrator to help give thata mission vibe.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:08:00,606" end="00:08:03,251">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">and I went waaaay back.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:08:03,251" end="00:08:05,752">- <span tts:fontStyle="italic">[Narrator] [clearing throat] </span></p>
      <p begin="00:08:05,752" end="00:08:09,679">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Once upon a timea single point exploded.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:08:09,679" end="00:08:11,196">[explosion]</p>
      <p begin="00:08:11,196" end="00:08:13,541">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">into the universe. </span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:08:13,541" end="00:08:16,361">[swishing sound]</p>
      <p begin="00:08:17,573" end="00:08:22,256">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Which caused the chain reaction that led to life.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:08:22,256" end="00:08:24,007">[thunder roaring]</p>
      <p begin="00:08:24,007" end="00:08:27,610">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">For a time dinosaurs lived large.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:08:27,610" end="00:08:28,982">[dinosaur wailing]</p>
      <p begin="00:08:28,982" end="00:08:29,766">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Then not so much.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:08:29,766" end="00:08:31,936">[splash]</p>
      <p begin="00:08:31,936" end="00:08:35,491">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">One theory of why they died out, is that they couldn't adapt</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:08:35,491" end="00:08:41,712">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">to the new flowering plantsthat depended on bees for pollination.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:08:41,712" end="00:08:45,947">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Bad news for the dinosaurs,good news for the bees.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:08:45,947" end="00:08:48,395">[bees buzzing]</p>
      <p begin="00:08:48,395" end="00:08:53,471">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Then a new group of very adaptable mammals emerged.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:08:53,471" end="00:08:59,557">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">They were social, lovable creatures who love to connect with each other.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:08:59,557" end="00:09:02,551">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">At first there were very few of them.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:09:02,551" end="00:09:06,924">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">But they had a couple of things going for them, their opposable thumbs</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:09:06,924" end="00:09:09,762">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">which were really goodat grasping stuff,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:09:09,762" end="00:09:12,710">[thud, thud, thud]</p>
      <p begin="00:09:12,710" end="00:09:14,067">[beep, beep, beep]</p>
      <p begin="00:09:14,067" end="00:09:20,692">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">and their unusually large brainswhich were exceptional at grasping ideas.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:09:20,692" end="00:09:22,918">[toink]</p>
      <p begin="00:09:22,918" end="00:09:26,286">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">The human brain grew rapidly in early evolution</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:09:26,286" end="00:09:30,023">not so that they could use tools<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>or expand their thinking,</p>
      <p begin="00:09:30,023" end="00:09:33,244">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">but because of their need to connect.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:09:33,244" end="00:09:36,330">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Because human babies are not fully developed,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:09:36,330" end="00:09:39,929">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">they rely on their parents longer than other species.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:09:39,929" end="00:09:46,811">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">So human brains evolvedto seek out human contact to survive.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:09:46,811" end="00:09:49,342">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">These brains are what distinguished humans</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:09:49,342" end="00:09:53,171">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">from the other two million species on earth.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:09:53,171" end="00:09:55,358">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">But for eons they couldn't communicate</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:09:55,358" end="00:09:58,223">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">much of what they knew about the world with others,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:09:58,223" end="00:10:00,078">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">because they had no written language.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:10:00,078" end="00:10:01,528">[gasping]</p>
      <p begin="00:10:01,528" end="00:10:02,803">[reed stick squeaking]</p>
      <p begin="00:10:02,803" end="00:10:06,639">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Then they finally invented a radical new technology</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:10:06,639" end="00:10:08,467">[creaking sound]</p>
      <p begin="00:10:08,467" end="00:10:10,137">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">that would change their lives forever.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:10:10,137" end="00:10:19,392">[pounding sound]</p>
      <p begin="00:10:19,392" end="00:10:23,959">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">The alphabet made it easier to keep a narrative record</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:10:23,959" end="00:10:25,739">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">to inform future generations</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:10:25,739" end="00:10:31,466">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">about what had happened and what had been learned.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:10:31,466" end="00:10:33,357">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">By accumulating knowledge, </span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:10:33,357" end="00:10:43,266">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">humans were able to progress and multiply.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:10:43,266" end="00:10:48,792">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">But literacy also led to something unexpected.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:10:48,792" end="00:10:51,034">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">In the "Alphabet Versus the Goddess" </span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:10:51,034" end="00:10:53,457">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Leonard Shlain points to how literacy changed</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:10:53,457" end="00:10:56,778">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">the way humans think.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:10:56,778" end="00:11:01,016">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">When the alphabet was introducedinto society, it over stimulated</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:11:01,016" end="00:11:04,410">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">the analytic left hemisphere of the brain. </span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:11:04,410" end="00:11:07,094">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">He builds on the theory that the left hemisphere</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:11:07,094" end="00:11:13,019">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">which is used in reading and writing is associated with masculine traits,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:11:13,019" end="00:11:16,440">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">and that the right hemisphere used to seeimages and patterns...</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:11:16,440" end="00:11:19,716">[humming]</p>
      <p begin="00:11:19,716" end="00:11:22,358">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">is more feminine.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:11:22,358" end="00:11:27,052">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">So Shlain suggests that the advent of literacy shifted the balance of power</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:11:27,052" end="00:11:30,923">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">between men and women.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:11:30,923" end="00:11:35,051">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Well in most ancient societiesmen worship the goddesses.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:11:35,051" end="00:11:38,136">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Whenever literacy was introduced into a society,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:11:38,136" end="00:11:43,520">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">a new patriarchal outlook emerged.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:11:43,520" end="00:11:46,394">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">He traced this patternthroughout history,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:11:46,394" end="00:11:49,114">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">finding links between the onset of literacy</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:11:49,114" end="00:11:56,085">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">and the oppression of women around the world.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:11:56,085" end="00:11:58,511">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">- Maybe there's a way to build on my father's ideas</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:11:58,511" end="00:12:00,922">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">about literacy and patriarchy.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:12:00,922" end="00:12:02,800">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">If he's saying that the invention of writing </span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:12:02,800" end="00:12:06,274">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">shifted us to a more analytical,left brain mode of thinking,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:12:06,274" end="00:12:11,728">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">maybe the shift also led to our tendency to think of world problems in isolation.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:12:11,728" end="00:12:14,629">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">I can't wait to call my father to see what he thought about this idea.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:12:14,629" end="00:12:25,952">[phone ringing]</p>
      <p begin="00:12:25,952" end="00:12:30,611">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">But no one picked up.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:12:30,611" end="00:12:33,050">[sirene wailing]</p>
      <p begin="00:12:38,396" end="00:12:40,149">[beeping]</p>
      <p begin="00:12:43,212" end="00:12:44,895">[beeping]</p>
      <p begin="00:12:53,065" end="00:13:05,048">[waves rumbling]</p>
      <p begin="00:13:05,048" end="00:13:10,097">[implosion]</p>
      <p begin="00:13:16,511" end="00:13:31,184">[whirring of camera]</p>
      <p begin="00:13:31,184" end="00:13:33,383">[explosion]</p>
      <p begin="00:13:37,075" end="00:13:46,151">[waves rumbling]</p>
      <p begin="00:13:46,151" end="00:13:49,216">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">I felt like a child again.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:13:51,960" end="00:13:53,517">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">I remember when I was four years old,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:13:53,517" end="00:13:57,287">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">we were skiing and we're on one of those really long chairlift rides.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:13:58,892" end="00:14:02,199">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">And I was just beginning to get on the ride and I slipped off</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:14:02,199" end="00:14:05,152">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">and my father grabbed the hood of my coat</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:14:05,152" end="00:14:07,468">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">and I was dangling from the chairliftand he was holding me</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:14:07,468" end="00:14:10,143">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">with everything he could.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:14:10,143" end="00:14:12,181">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">We were up 40 feet and there was snow beneath us </span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:14:12,181" end="00:14:15,619">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">but we could seerocky cliffs just ahead.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:14:15,619" end="00:14:18,664">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">And he looked at me and said, "I can't hold on to you the whole way."</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:14:18,664" end="00:14:21,088">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">"It's safer to let you go here over the snow."</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:14:21,873" end="00:14:25,843">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">And I kept saying, "Daddy, Daddy, don't let me go!"</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:14:25,843" end="00:14:30,455">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">And he looked into my eyes and he said, "You're gonna be okay."</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:14:30,455" end="00:14:32,028">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">And then he dropped me.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:14:32,182" end="00:14:34,009">[thud]</p>
      <p begin="00:14:38,119" end="00:14:39,993">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">He had to.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:14:46,523" end="00:14:50,405">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">And here I was suddenly feeling the same way,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:14:50,405" end="00:14:54,462">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">like, "Daddy don't let me go."</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:14:54,462" end="00:14:58,726">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">I couldn't imagine my world without him.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:15:02,748" end="00:15:04,599">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Those first few days while he was in the hospital</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:15:04,599" end="00:15:10,149">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">recovering from brain surgery,everybody had advice.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:15:10,149" end="00:15:13,565">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">I spoke to this good friend of mine who had lost his father,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:15:13,565" end="00:15:18,579">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">he said the most important thing he could tell me was to film my Dad.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:15:18,579" end="00:15:21,179">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">It was his biggest regretthat he hadn't recorded his father</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:15:21,179" end="00:15:25,150">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">before it was too late.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:15:25,150" end="00:15:29,164">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">I knew I had to startas soon as possible.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:15:30,318" end="00:15:32,160">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">But even though I'd made a lot of films,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:15:32,160" end="00:15:36,784">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">I was at a lost on how to capturemy father's essence on film.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:15:36,784" end="00:15:42,461">[waves crashing]</p>
      <p begin="00:15:42,461" end="00:15:44,382">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">My father always said we're the only species</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:15:44,382" end="00:15:46,352">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">that knows we're gonna die,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:15:46,352" end="00:15:50,569">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">and that so much of what we dois driven by that knowledge.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:15:53,763" end="00:15:55,405">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">My mother would say emotional connection</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:15:55,405" end="00:15:59,061">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">is what drives everything we do.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:16:00,308" end="00:16:02,223">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">I thought I understood what they meant.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:16:04,541" end="00:16:05,714">[thunder roaring]</p>
      <p begin="00:16:05,714" end="00:16:09,299">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Death is really abstract until someoneyou love is dying right in front of you.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:16:19,848" end="00:16:21,730">[rattling sound]</p>
      <p begin="00:16:21,730" end="00:16:25,252">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">And then a few days after my fatherwas given around nine months to live,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:16:25,252" end="00:16:27,350">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">my husband Ken and I found that I was pregnant.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:16:29,366" end="00:16:33,616">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">But we had been through five miscarriages.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:16:41,819" end="00:16:43,727">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">We'd had an easy time havingour first child.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:16:43,727" end="00:16:48,558">- [Girl] &#9834; Twinkle twinkle little star<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>How I wonder what you are. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:16:50,628" end="00:16:54,806">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">But having a second child turned out to be a lot more difficult.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:16:56,206" end="00:17:00,084">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Everything felt out of my control,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:17:02,132" end="00:17:05,648">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">except when I was working on the film.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:17:05,648" end="00:17:14,665">&#9834; [music] &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:17:14,665" end="00:17:18,342">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Everything we've been thinking about suddenly became much more urgent.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:17:18,396" end="00:17:20,284">[explosion]</p>
      <p begin="00:17:20,392" end="00:17:22,409">[water gushing]</p>
      <p begin="00:17:22,505" end="00:17:25,253">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">What kind of world are we handlingto the next generation?</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:17:25,296" end="00:17:26,375">[explosion]</p>
      <p begin="00:17:26,375" end="00:17:27,761">[people shouting]</p>
      <p begin="00:17:29,322" end="00:17:32,921">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">We as humans have accumulatedso much knowledge.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:17:32,921" end="00:17:35,963">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Why do we have such a hard timeseeing the bigger picture?</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:17:35,963" end="00:17:38,051">[clapping sounds]</p>
      <p begin="00:17:38,051" end="00:17:47,883">&#9834; [music] &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:17:47,883" end="00:17:51,519">- <span tts:fontStyle="italic">As humans in western civilization progressed,</span></p>
      <p begin="00:17:51,519" end="00:17:58,007">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">men dominated, and so did left hemisphere thinking.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:17:58,007" end="00:18:01,770">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Whenever a problem arose,their strategy was to break it down</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:18:01,770" end="00:18:07,583">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">into simple parts to solve it.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:18:07,583" end="00:18:14,366">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">They divided and sub-divided, isolated and analyzed.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:18:14,366" end="00:18:17,186">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">They formulated theories about their discoveries</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:18:17,186" end="00:18:21,144">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">and developed a method to test those theories.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:18:21,144" end="00:18:26,740"><span tts:fontStyle="italic">They called it</span> science<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/><span tts:fontStyle="italic">after the Greek word meaning</span> to cut.</p>
      <p begin="00:18:26,740" end="00:18:28,404">[cheering and applause]</p>
      <p begin="00:18:28,404" end="00:18:32,473">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">This strategy worked so well that they began slicing and dicing</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:18:32,473" end="00:18:35,856">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">everything they discovered.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:18:35,856" end="00:18:38,992">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Classifying and breaking down everything around them,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:18:38,992" end="00:18:42,869">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">became a whole way of seeing the world.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:18:42,869" end="00:18:48,956">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">For example, they divided beasts into hundreds of sub-categories.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:18:48,956" end="00:18:52,277">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">A vision of division.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:18:52,277" end="00:18:57,137"><span tts:fontStyle="italic">They even classified their own species,which they named</span> homo-sapiens,</p>
      <p begin="00:18:57,137" end="00:19:02,635">meaning wise being <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/><span tts:fontStyle="italic">since they were such wise guys.</span></p>
      <p begin="00:19:02,635" end="00:19:05,700">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Their cleverness helped them to believe that they were different </span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:19:05,700" end="00:19:07,834">from other species.</p>
      <p begin="00:19:07,834" end="00:19:14,845">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">So much so that they began thinking ofthemselves as independent from nature.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:19:14,845" end="00:19:17,968">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Entirely.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:19:17,968" end="00:19:20,272">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Very left brain.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:19:20,272" end="00:19:28,066">[clicking sounds]</p>
      <p begin="00:19:28,066" end="00:19:32,717">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">- My father's tumor was on the left side of his brain, in the speech center.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:19:32,717" end="00:19:36,674">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">When he came out of surgeryhe couldn't speak at all.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:19:36,674" end="00:19:41,386">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">The doctors didn't know if his speech would ever come back.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:19:41,386" end="00:19:43,546">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">I was worried, I would never hear his voice again,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:19:45,894" end="00:19:51,081">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">and that I had already lost my chance to film him.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:19:51,081" end="00:19:58,268">[phone ringing]</p>
      <p begin="00:19:58,268" end="00:20:00,186">[answering machine] <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Hi, this is Leonard Shlain,</span></p>
      <p begin="00:20:00,186" end="00:20:04,629">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">please leave your name and your telephone number very slowly.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:20:04,629" end="00:20:06,925">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Thank you so much, bye.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:20:06,925" end="00:20:09,354">[dial tone]</p>
      <p begin="00:20:09,354" end="00:20:11,307">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">- I was so used to calling him every morning</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:20:11,307" end="00:20:13,754">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">to talk about everything that was going on</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:20:13,754" end="00:20:16,525">and it was really hard not to.</p>
      <p begin="00:20:18,033" end="00:20:21,247">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">There was so much going through my head.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:20:21,247" end="00:20:26,354">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">What kind of world have we created where we have this epidemic of cancer?</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:20:26,354" end="00:20:30,202">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">What's causing it?</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:20:30,202" end="00:20:34,220">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">I mean we're directing all these radiation right at our heads.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:20:34,220" end="00:20:37,666">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">What are studies gonna say ten years from now about cellphones and cancer?</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:20:37,666" end="00:20:39,914">[spraying sound]</p>
      <p begin="00:20:39,914" end="00:20:42,592">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Or the toxins and pesticides and stress?</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:20:42,592" end="00:20:45,274">[shuffling paper]</p>
      <p begin="00:20:45,274" end="00:20:48,680">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">All the same things we're talking aboutwith the disappearance of honeybees.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:20:48,680" end="00:20:50,654">[buzzing]</p>
      <p begin="00:20:50,654" end="00:20:51,999">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">What are the bees telling us?</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:20:51,999" end="00:20:53,153">[slap]</p>
      <p begin="00:20:55,108" end="00:20:58,638">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Maybe we're all working too hard.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:20:58,638" end="00:21:02,144">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">And my father, he definitely worked his brain hard.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:21:02,144" end="00:21:06,395">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">I kept wondering, did he stretch his mindinto too many unusual places?</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:21:07,434" end="00:21:10,944">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">I know it's not rational but I still think about it.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:21:10,944" end="00:21:13,682">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">And not being able to talk to him right then was specially hard,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:21:13,682" end="00:21:17,971">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">because Ken and I had always gone to him for advice.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:21:17,971" end="00:21:22,158">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">And here I was at the beginning of this high-risk pregnancy.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:21:22,158" end="00:21:23,117">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">We had all these test </span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:21:23,117" end="00:21:27,097">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">and we wouldn't know if it would hold for another three months.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:21:28,166" end="00:21:32,345">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">And of course, we were really nervous because of my history,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:21:32,345" end="00:21:34,529">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">not to mention the fact that there are three hundred chemicals</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:21:34,529" end="00:21:38,101">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">found in umbilical cord blood.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:21:38,101" end="00:21:41,838">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">and half of them are believed to cause cancer,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:21:41,944" end="00:21:43,705">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">like mercury.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:21:46,131" end="00:21:48,249">[thundering]</p>
      <p begin="00:21:48,249" end="00:21:49,931">[water falling]</p>
      <p begin="00:21:49,931" end="00:21:51,765">[zoom]</p>
      <p begin="00:21:51,765" end="00:21:53,532">[chimes]</p>
      <p begin="00:21:53,532" end="00:21:56,800">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">After all the miscarriages,I finally was trying in vitro</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:21:56,800" end="00:22:00,664">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">and this was our thirdand final attempt.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:22:02,646" end="00:22:04,521">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">We had our first ultrasound appointment a few weeks</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:22:04,521" end="00:22:08,374">after my father was released<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>from the hospital.</p>
      <p begin="00:22:08,374" end="00:22:10,772">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">He still couldn't speak clearlybut it was a big moment,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:22:10,772" end="00:22:14,515">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">and he and my stepmother Anareally wanted to come.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:22:14,515" end="00:22:19,683">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">The doctor turned on the monitor,I was pregnant with twins.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:22:19,683" end="00:22:21,716">[lub dub lub dub]</p>
      <p begin="00:22:21,716" end="00:22:24,427">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">It was such a relief after everything we'd gone through.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:22:24,427" end="00:22:27,096">[heart beating]</p>
      <p begin="00:22:27,096" end="00:22:33,656">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">All the visits to the hospital, the tests, the shots and uncertainty...</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:22:33,656" end="00:22:38,390">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">My experience was so much different from my mother's generation.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:22:38,390" end="00:22:39,280">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">She used to say,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:22:39,280" end="00:22:44,990">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">"I'd get nauseous, gain weight,and nine months later I'd have a baby."</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:22:44,990" end="00:22:48,674">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">But it wasn't all that simple for her either.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:22:48,674" end="00:22:51,292">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">My mother wanted to have a career but felt that she had to choose</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:22:51,292" end="00:22:54,129">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">between children and work.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:22:59,130" end="00:23:03,237">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">It wasn't until after she raised us and my parents got divorced,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:23:03,237" end="00:23:07,173">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">that she got a PhD in Psychology.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:23:07,173" end="00:23:09,324">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">I, on the other hand wanted to have my career established</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:23:09,324" end="00:23:12,348">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">before I started to have children.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:23:13,799" end="00:23:17,847">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Growing up my father wanted us allto become doctors.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:23:17,847" end="00:23:19,398">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">He even bought my sister and me,the book,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:23:19,398" end="00:23:24,879">The Making of a Woman Surgeon,<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/><span tts:fontStyle="italic">four times.</span></p>
      <p begin="00:23:24,879" end="00:23:27,740">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">But I didn't want to become a doctor.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:23:27,740" end="00:23:30,875">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">I was fascinated with film makingand how film and technology</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:23:30,875" end="00:23:34,309">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">can connect people around the world.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:23:34,309" end="00:23:39,130">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">In 1984, my Dad gave me a Macintosh.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:23:39,130" end="00:23:41,417">It was right after my parents <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>got divorced.</p>
      <p begin="00:23:41,417" end="00:23:43,921">[explosion]</p>
      <p begin="00:23:43,921" end="00:23:46,638">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">And in the middle of my parents' separation,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:23:46,638" end="00:23:50,816">that computer was my link <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>to another world.</p>
      <p begin="00:23:51,907" end="00:23:54,002">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">I had a modem and I would connect to the library, </span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:23:54,002" end="00:23:57,901">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">which was really exciting at the time.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:23:58,951" end="00:24:02,736">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Then in the late 80's still well before the world wide web was created,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:24:02,736" end="00:24:05,280">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">my friend and I wrote this proposal in high school</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:24:05,280" end="00:24:07,002">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">about how students from enemy countries</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:24:07,002" end="00:24:10,294">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">could communicate through their computers.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:24:10,294" end="00:24:11,857"><span tts:fontStyle="italic">We called it</span> UNITAS.</p>
      <p begin="00:24:11,857" end="00:24:14,088">[beep, beep, beep]</p>
      <p begin="00:24:14,088" end="00:24:19,205">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">I was invited to be a student ambassador to take that idea to the Soviet Union.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:24:19,205" end="00:24:23,560">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">But once there, my bubble just totally burst.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:24:23,560" end="00:24:25,916">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">I was so naive in thinking that people will have computers </span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:24:25,916" end="00:24:31,753">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">when there was barely enough food.It was a big wake up call for me.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:24:31,753" end="00:24:33,979">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Then in 1994 someone said to me,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:24:33,979" end="00:24:36,899">"You have to see this thing <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>called the Web."</p>
      <p begin="00:24:36,899" end="00:24:39,324">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">It was love at first sight.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:24:40,395" end="00:24:44,765">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Here finally was this frameworkfor a global conversation, </span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:24:44,765" end="00:24:47,342">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">I was blown away.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:24:47,342" end="00:24:49,178">[doink]</p>
      <p begin="00:24:49,178" end="00:24:52,198">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">I started the Webby Awards and spent the next decade focused on the web</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:24:52,198" end="00:24:53,720">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">and where it was taking us.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:24:53,720" end="00:24:57,725">We all know that the true <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>international language is HTML.</p>
      <p begin="00:24:57,725" end="00:25:00,756">- We all invented the Internet.</p>
      <p begin="00:25:00,756" end="00:25:03,509">&#9834; [music] &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:25:03,509" end="00:25:06,486">- Oscar, Emmys, Grammys, Tonys,<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>the big award shows</p>
      <p begin="00:25:06,486" end="00:25:08,413">all have one thing in common --</p>
      <p begin="00:25:08,413" end="00:25:10,318">endless acceptance speeches.</p>
      <p begin="00:25:10,318" end="00:25:11,233">So we can all be glad the people</p>
      <p begin="00:25:11,233" end="00:25:14,747">who run the Webbys, the awards <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>for websites have found a way</p>
      <p begin="00:25:14,747" end="00:25:16,632">to keep those speeches short.</p>
      <p begin="00:25:16,632" end="00:25:20,424">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">- All acceptance speeches must be five words or less.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:25:20,424" end="00:25:24,481"><span tts:fontStyle="italic">- Please don't recount this vote.</span><br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>[audience shouting]</p>
      <p begin="00:25:24,481" end="00:25:28,331">- <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Then I met Ken at one of my Dad's talksin arts and physics.</span></p>
      <p begin="00:25:28,331" end="00:25:30,557">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Ken was a robotics professor who also</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:25:30,557" end="00:25:32,757">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">did art installationthat connected robots</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:25:32,757" end="00:25:37,250">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">to the Internet, to gardens, to make commentary on society.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:25:37,250" end="00:25:40,005">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">He was my true love at first sight.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:25:40,005" end="00:25:46,001">- Professor Ken Goldberg wants to come up<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>and - [audience shouts]</p>
      <p begin="00:25:46,001" end="00:25:49,054">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">...and end our hosting portion, Ken.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:25:49,054" end="00:25:54,391">- Thank you Albert. Mazel Tov <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>in this very important occasion.</p>
      <p begin="00:25:54,391" end="00:25:56,741">And today you answered <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>one of the most important questions</p>
      <p begin="00:25:56,741" end="00:26:02,439">of your life, by saying I do.</p>
      <p begin="00:26:02,439" end="00:26:05,234">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">[Ken] So right now, I'd like to ask you another question.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:26:05,234" end="00:26:06,751">[audience] Uh-oh.</p>
      <p begin="00:26:06,751" end="00:26:10,843">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">[Ken] May I have your daughter Tiffany's hand?</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:26:10,843" end="00:26:19,748">[cheers and applause]</p>
      <p begin="00:26:19,748" end="00:26:22,576">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">- You just saved a lot of money, the rabbi's still here ---</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:26:22,576" end="00:26:27,564">[laughter and applause]</p>
      <p begin="00:26:27,564" end="00:26:28,252">- [Tiffany] <span tts:fontStyle="italic">My Dad always said,</span></p>
      <p begin="00:26:28,252" end="00:26:32,538">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">"I wrote out in physics so you and Ken would meet."</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:26:32,538" end="00:26:35,822">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Ken and I had our first child, Odessa when I was 33.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:26:35,822" end="00:26:39,158">- lessem<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>- alahum</p>
      <p begin="00:26:39,158" end="00:26:41,071">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">As a working mom, I felt the Internet was the tool</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:26:41,071" end="00:26:43,554">the feminist movement had always needed</p>
      <p begin="00:26:43,554" end="00:26:46,981">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">because I had so much flexibility in how and where I can work.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:26:46,981" end="00:26:48,008">[child] Mommy!</p>
      <p begin="00:26:48,008" end="00:26:50,508">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">[man's voice] Ahhh,that's pretty amazing.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:26:50,508" end="00:26:55,626">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">But after 35, the chances of having a successful pregnancy is cut in half.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:26:55,626" end="00:26:57,961">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">We waited too long to have our second child.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:26:57,961" end="00:27:00,938">[clock ticking]</p>
      <p begin="00:27:00,938" end="00:27:04,791">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">I had trusted too much that science will extend my fertility,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:27:04,791" end="00:27:06,265">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">And now I was trying hormone treatments</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:27:06,265" end="00:27:11,311">that I didn't even know <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>all the consequences of.</p>
      <p begin="00:27:11,311" end="00:27:14,420">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">I remember walking down the street one day with my core film crew.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:27:14,420" end="00:27:17,292">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Telling them I was starting another round of in vitro,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:27:17,292" end="00:27:18,871">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">I was gonna start taking estrogen shots,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:27:18,871" end="00:27:22,753">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">so my mood might be a little all over the place.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:27:22,753" end="00:27:24,246">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">And then Sawyer who was transitioning</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:27:24,246" end="00:27:27,806">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">from female to male said, "Well that's funny,"</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:27:27,806" end="00:27:29,582">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">"because I was just about to tell you, too,"</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:27:29,582" end="00:27:32,332">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">that I'm gonna start taking testosterone shots.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:27:32,332" end="00:27:35,092">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">So my mood might be all over the place, too."</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:27:35,092" end="00:27:36,290">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">And Carlton who's walking between us </span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:27:36,290" end="00:27:39,175">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">turns to me and said, "Wait let me get this straight,"</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:27:39,175" end="00:27:43,393">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">"You're going on estrogen and you're going on testosterone."</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:27:43,393" end="00:27:44,393">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">"I'm going on vacation."</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:27:44,393" end="00:27:47,457">&#9834; [music] &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:27:47,457" end="00:27:50,198">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">So things are clearly changing,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:27:50,198" end="00:27:52,860">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">There's so much more to think about.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:27:52,860" end="00:27:57,141">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">And that piece of change is only exhilarating.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:27:57,141" end="00:28:00,347">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">How much faster can I go before we can't keep up?</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:28:00,347" end="00:28:03,186">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">And how do things start moving so quickly, to begin with?</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:28:03,186" end="00:28:08,605">[cogwheels whirring]</p>
      <p begin="00:28:10,482" end="00:28:13,219">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">- [Narrator] Thanks to human's analytic way of thinking,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:28:13,219" end="00:28:17,084">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">progress toward a better quality of life accelerated.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:28:17,084" end="00:28:20,544">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">As they progress, their numbers grew.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:28:20,544" end="00:28:23,753">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">And as more and more humans populated the world, </span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:28:23,753" end="00:28:27,205">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">more and more ideas interacted.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:28:27,205" end="00:28:29,061">[thunder roaring]</p>
      <p begin="00:28:29,061" end="00:28:34,652">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">New inventions and new discoveries happening faster and faster.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:28:34,652" end="00:28:39,215">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">The ancient Greeks had a God of Speed, his name is Mercury.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:28:39,215" end="00:28:46,606">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Mercury is also the name of an element, a car and a rock star.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:28:46,606" end="00:28:50,984">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Humans were entering a time of unparalleled discovery</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:28:52,231" end="00:28:56,038">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">And there was still so much to explore.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:28:56,038" end="00:28:59,936">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">So they divided the world up into a giant grid</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:28:59,936" end="00:29:04,061">to navigate unchartered territories.</p>
      <p begin="00:29:04,061" end="00:29:12,272">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">The idea was simple.Divide and conquer, for better or worse.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:29:14,595" end="00:29:16,657">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">But something interesting happened.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:29:16,657" end="00:29:18,152">[flapping sound]</p>
      <p begin="00:29:18,235" end="00:29:22,497">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">As they were dividing up the worldinto separate territories</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:29:22,497" end="00:29:27,941">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">the world was becoming more connectedthan ever before.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:29:27,941" end="00:29:31,725">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Even though the world's ecosystem had always been interdependent,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:29:31,725" end="00:29:35,278">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">now humans were integrating trade, transportation </span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:29:35,278" end="00:29:37,904">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">and idea networks into it.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:29:39,797" end="00:29:43,742">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">They traded everythingincluding species.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:29:43,742" end="00:29:48,370">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">For example, the Europeans brought their honeybees to the Americas</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:29:48,370" end="00:29:50,863">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">to help out in the fields.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:29:50,863" end="00:29:54,334">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">The western way of dividing and specializing was spreading</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:29:54,334" end="00:29:57,947">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">around the world through these new channels</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:29:57,947" end="00:30:00,200">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Thanks in partto one particular invention</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:30:00,200" end="00:30:02,157">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">which could reproduce,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:30:02,157" end="00:30:06,138">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">and help circulate ideaslike never before.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:30:07,692" end="00:30:13,551">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Powerful, controversial ideas like democracy,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:30:13,551" end="00:30:17,522">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Charles Darwin's theory that all life is connected.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:30:17,522" end="00:30:20,530">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">And political scientistNicolas de Condorcet's</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:30:20,530" end="00:30:24,030">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">idea of the powerof collective thinking.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:30:24,030" end="00:30:27,505">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Which proved that a group of mindswas more often correct</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:30:27,505" end="00:30:31,144">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">than a single mindthinking independently,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:30:31,144" end="00:30:34,944">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">and formed the basis of the jury system.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:30:36,821" end="00:30:39,003">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Ideas were spreading so fast</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:30:39,003" end="00:30:44,581"><span tts:fontStyle="italic">that these wise beings called it,</span><br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>The Age of Enlightenment.</p>
      <p begin="00:30:44,581" end="00:30:49,428">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Economies grew and networks expanded.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:30:49,428" end="00:30:52,571">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Soon enough these clever humans figured out that they could apply</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:30:52,571" end="00:30:58,628">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic"> their method of Divide and Conquer to meet new consumer demands.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:30:59,444" end="00:31:02,746">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">These amazing new method of productions spread from England</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:31:02,746" end="00:31:04,882">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">around the globe.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:31:04,882" end="00:31:11,595">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">And they were catapulted into an era of mass production and abundance.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:31:11,595" end="00:31:14,550">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">This new efficiency gave them a lot more free time,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:31:14,550" end="00:31:15,919">[splash] <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>[girls shrieking]</p>
      <p begin="00:31:17,570" end="00:31:20,202">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">And the establishment of an official weekend.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:31:20,202" end="00:31:22,792">[cheering]</p>
      <p begin="00:31:23,707" end="00:31:28,295">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">During the Industrial Revolution,they predicted that by the 20th century,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:31:28,295" end="00:31:33,342">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic"> they'd be so efficient that they would only be working four hours a day.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:31:33,342" end="00:31:35,788">&#9834; [humming] &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:31:35,819" end="00:31:37,171">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Hmmm...</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:31:37,171" end="00:31:39,464">[buzzing]</p>
      <p begin="00:31:41,656" end="00:31:48,668">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">But one particular discovery held the promise to radically change the world.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:31:48,668" end="00:31:51,575">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">A scientist named Marie Curie discovered</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:31:51,575" end="00:31:55,081">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic"> that an element called Uranium emitted energy</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:31:55,081" end="00:31:58,331">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">when its tiniest components break apart.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:32:00,224" end="00:32:05,161">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">People all around the world hoped that this radioactive energy could provide</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:32:05,161" end="00:32:08,374">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">a miraculous and limitless new source of energy</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:32:08,374" end="00:32:14,281">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">that could be used in the name of progress.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:32:14,785" end="00:32:17,182">[train chugging]</p>
      <p begin="00:32:17,182" end="00:32:20,324">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">- [Tiffany] But somethingunexpected happened.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:32:20,324" end="00:32:23,223">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Marie Curie also stumbled upon the first</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:32:23,233" end="00:32:26,323">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">treatment for cancersusing radio activity.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:32:29,943" end="00:32:33,574">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">My father's radiation treatmentwas working and he was getting better.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:32:35,881" end="00:32:37,717">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">His speech was starting to come back</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:32:37,717" end="00:32:42,015">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">but he wasn't able to articulate very clearly.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:32:42,015" end="00:32:43,279">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">I didn't know how much time we're gonna have</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:32:43,279" end="00:32:47,351">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">and I started bringing around my camera wherever we went.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:32:47,351" end="00:32:54,572">- So then if we gave you, clips of...<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>of uhmm....</p>
      <p begin="00:32:59,296" end="00:33:03,773">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">- But it was really frustrating for him because his words kept coming out wrong.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:33:04,546" end="00:33:07,529">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">As a surgeon who operated on and wrote about the brain.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:33:07,529" end="00:33:11,824">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">He knew exactly whythat was happening.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:33:11,824" end="00:33:13,845">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Just before he was diagnosedwith brain cancer,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:33:13,845" end="00:33:15,939">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">my father was writing the last chapterof the book</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:33:15,939" end="00:33:18,836">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">he'd been working on for five years.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:33:18,836" end="00:33:21,214"><span tts:fontStyle="italic">It was called</span> Leonardo's Brain*</p>
      <p begin="00:33:21,214" end="00:33:26,662">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">and a look at how Leonardo Da Vinci was able to master both art and science.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:33:26,662" end="00:33:28,602">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">He was so determined to finish that book</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:33:28,602" end="00:33:31,802">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">and even though he wasstill having trouble talking,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:33:31,802" end="00:33:38,195">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">he was able to write.It just took longer.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:33:38,195" end="00:33:42,242">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">He mentioned that suddenly he was noticing patterns like never before.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:33:44,744" end="00:33:47,578">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">He loved to just sit and look out the window.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:33:47,578" end="00:33:57,381">[seagulls squawking]</p>
      <p begin="00:33:57,381" end="00:34:01,775">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">He even wrote about what he was seeing.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:34:05,427" end="00:34:07,269">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">The irony kept getting stronger</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:34:07,269" end="00:34:10,168">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">that as we were all focused24/7 on Leonard's brain,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:34:10,168" end="00:34:14,242">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">he was writing about "Leonardo's Brain,"</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:34:18,012" end="00:34:22,179">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">When we could find extra time, I tried to film him.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:34:22,179" end="00:34:23,634">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">He really want us to do the interviews</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:34:23,634" end="00:34:25,333">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">and even though there were a lot of pauses</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:34:25,333" end="00:34:28,938">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">in his speech, he was getting much stronger.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:34:28,938" end="00:34:30,080">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">He joked to the family,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:34:30,080" end="00:34:34,795">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">"I always wanted you to hang on to my every word."</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:34:34,795" end="00:34:38,594">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Of course every imaginable technical problem came up.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:34:38,594" end="00:34:42,960">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">One time it was the sound, or the lighting</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:34:42,960" end="00:34:47,164">and sometimes I would just become <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>an emotional basket case.</p>
      <p begin="00:34:47,164" end="00:34:53,831">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Okay, so what have you learned to - what have you learned that might --</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:34:53,831" end="00:34:58,246">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">What if I switch again to being your child?</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:34:58,246" end="00:35:01,682">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Other times I'd hold it together but he was just too weak.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:35:01,682" end="00:35:04,491">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">What do you think that the meaning of life is?</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:35:04,491" end="00:35:07,900">- The meaning of life...</p>
      <p begin="00:35:07,900" end="00:35:10,147">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">And regardless, this wasn't the image</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:35:10,147" end="00:35:12,247">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">I wanted to hold on to,he was my superhero.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:35:12,247" end="00:35:13,845">[drums beating]</p>
      <p begin="00:35:13,845" end="00:35:17,337">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">I remember when I was sixteen and I had just gotten my driver's license.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:35:17,337" end="00:35:21,952">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">That feeling of ultimate independence being able to drive myself somewhere,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:35:21,952" end="00:35:24,757">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">and I was on the Golden Gate bridge and I had the music blasting,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:35:24,757" end="00:35:27,589">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">and maybe I wasn't paying asmuch attention as I should have.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:35:27,589" end="00:35:30,066">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">And then the person in front of me slammed on the breaks,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:35:30,066" end="00:35:31,912">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">and I didn't have enough time to stop,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:35:31,912" end="00:35:34,034">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">and I bumped right into the back of the car,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:35:34,034" end="00:35:37,811">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">and got into an accident on the Golden Gate bridge</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:35:37,811" end="00:35:40,699">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">with this fresh green driver's license.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:35:40,699" end="00:35:42,577">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">I was shaking, I didn't know what to do,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:35:42,577" end="00:35:47,151">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">I got out of my car causing this huge traffic jam.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:35:47,151" end="00:35:50,863">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">When my father came out of nowhere,it was almost like he had a cape</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:35:50,863" end="00:35:51,590">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">And he arrived and said;</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:35:51,590" end="00:35:54,856">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">"Honey get back in the car, I'll take care of things."</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:35:54,856" end="00:35:57,408">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">I didn't know it but he had been right behind me all along</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:35:57,408" end="00:36:00,503">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">watching the way I was driving.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:36:00,503" end="00:36:02,683">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">There have been many instances when a crisis happens</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:36:02,683" end="00:36:04,409">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">and I'm kind of lookingover my shoulders,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:36:04,409" end="00:36:10,668">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">hoping he's gonna stride up and give me some guidance on what to do.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:36:16,540" end="00:36:21,571">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">And there I was three months pregnant still needing his guidance.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:36:21,571" end="00:36:25,547">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Ken and I went in for the bigthree-month doctor's appointment.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:36:25,547" end="00:36:27,895">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">The doctor turned on the sonogram and we listened.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:36:27,895" end="00:36:29,802">[heart beating]</p>
      <p begin="00:36:29,802" end="00:36:33,216"><span tts:fontStyle="italic">There was only one heart beat.</span><br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>[beating]</p>
      <p begin="00:36:33,216" end="00:36:35,388">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">One of the twins had died.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:36:35,388" end="00:36:40,049">[heart beating]<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>&#9834; [music] &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:36:41,558" end="00:36:44,390">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">We wondered, will the other heart beat stop, too?</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:36:44,390" end="00:36:50,030">&#9834; [music] &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:36:50,030" end="00:36:53,147">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">But the doctor said, that actually it willstrengthen the remaining</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:36:53,157" end="00:36:56,525">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">baby's odds for survival.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:36:57,142" end="00:36:58,324">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">I tried to remind myself,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:36:58,324" end="00:37:01,724">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">if it wasn't meant to beit wasn't meant to be.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:37:01,724" end="00:37:06,138">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">I tried focusing on the new life and our five year old daughter, Odessa</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:37:06,138" end="00:37:08,715">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">and beating the odds.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:37:11,377" end="00:37:13,148">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Ken and I even named our daughter Odessa</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:37:13,148" end="00:37:18,320">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">in honor of the fact that both of our families have beaten the odds.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:37:18,320" end="00:37:20,390">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Our grandparents were Jews from Odessa on the Ukraine</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:37:20,390" end="00:37:23,512">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">who fled during the Russian revolution.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:37:23,512" end="00:37:25,258">My grandfather was woken up <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>in the middle of the night</p>
      <p begin="00:37:25,258" end="00:37:29,112">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">by his dad and put on the back of a hay truck.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:37:29,112" end="00:37:31,271">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">His father told him to go America and make enough money</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:37:31,271" end="00:37:34,176">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">to bring the whole family over.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:37:35,254" end="00:37:40,260">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">And so he did and he sent money every month for years.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:37:40,260" end="00:37:46,596"><span tts:fontStyle="italic">Until he found out that his whole family had died in the</span> Holocaust.</p>
      <p begin="00:37:47,427" end="00:37:50,812">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">But my grandfather beat the odds.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:37:56,741" end="00:38:00,257">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">And my Dad needed to beat the odds.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:38:02,077" end="00:38:05,939">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">And it seemed like we as a species needed to beat the odds.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:38:07,117" end="00:38:11,553">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">My father used to say it's one of the greatest paradoxes of humans,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:38:11,553" end="00:38:14,184">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">that we're simultaneously the most compassionate</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:38:14,184" end="00:38:17,316">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">and the most cruel of any species.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:38:18,155" end="00:38:22,639">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">How can we tap into our connectednessto overcome our self-destructive impulses?</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:38:23,299" end="00:38:29,473">[gun shots]<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>[explosion]</p>
      <p begin="00:38:29,853" end="00:38:33,504">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">- [Narrator] By 1914 the world had become so connected</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:38:33,504" end="00:38:35,811">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">that one assassination in Europe,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:38:35,811" end="00:38:42,034">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">launched a global war that extended to every continent on earth,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:38:42,034" end="00:38:45,251">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">and that one death led to fifteen million more.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:38:45,251" end="00:38:47,290">[gunshots and explosion]</p>
      <p begin="00:38:47,290" end="00:38:50,331">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">The war was so devastating that when it finally ended</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:38:50,331" end="00:38:53,825">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">it was declared, the war to end all wars.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:38:53,825" end="00:38:57,928">[crowd chanting]</p>
      <p begin="00:38:57,928" end="00:39:02,168">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">That eternal peace lasted fifteen years,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:39:04,835" end="00:39:09,219">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">and sixteen million more human beings died.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:39:11,360" end="00:39:14,535">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">World War II was the deadliest conflict in human history.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:39:14,535" end="00:39:20,439">[bomb exploding]</p>
      <p begin="00:39:20,439" end="00:39:22,699">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">The more connected humans became,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:39:22,699" end="00:39:27,366">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">the greater the consequencesof their actions.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:39:27,366" end="00:39:31,659">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">What would Madam Curie have thought?</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:39:31,659" end="00:39:33,505">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">in any interdependent system,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:39:33,505" end="00:39:38,272">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">every action leads to a chain reaction.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:39:38,272" end="00:39:39,338">[explosions]</p>
      <p begin="00:39:39,338" end="00:39:42,790">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Like in 1958, China's leader Chairman Mao</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:39:42,790" end="00:39:45,878">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">initiated the great leap forward.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:39:45,878" end="00:39:48,596">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">A campaign for progress.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:39:48,596" end="00:39:52,409">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">He wanted to eradicate the sparrows.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:39:52,409" end="00:39:58,479">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Sparrows he argued, disrupted agriculture,because they ate grain seeds.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:39:58,479" end="00:40:03,412">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">So they tore down the sparrow's nests, broke the eggs and killed the nestlings.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:40:05,304" end="00:40:07,842">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">At first then harvest improved,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:40:07,842" end="00:40:11,793">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">but a few years later, somethingunpredictable happened.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:40:11,793" end="00:40:15,644">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Suddenly, locusts populations exploded</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:40:15,644" end="00:40:19,727">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">because the sparrows weren't there to eat them.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:40:19,727" end="00:40:25,416">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">This led to a chain reaction that destroyed the country's food supply.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:40:25,416" end="00:40:32,043">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Thirty-six millions humans died of starvation in three years.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:40:34,043" end="00:40:40,797">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">But sometimes even negative events can lead to unexpected positive outcomes.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:40:40,797" end="00:40:44,805">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">- [Announcer] One of the years that completely reshaped the world we know.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:40:44,805" end="00:40:47,994">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Man took a giant strideinto the age of the atom</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:40:47,994" end="00:40:51,478">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">and science had the moon in its grasp.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:40:51,528" end="00:40:54,076"><span tts:fontStyle="italic">Take the</span> Cold War --</p>
      <p begin="00:40:55,115" end="00:40:58,085">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">a competition between the United States and the Soviet Union</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:40:59,208" end="00:41:03,921">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">which led to two of many monumental developments.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:41:03,921" end="00:41:08,238">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Development #. 1 -- the U.S.' drive to go to the moon,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:41:08,238" end="00:41:13,217">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">which resulted in the first photo of the earth from outer space.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:41:15,137" end="00:41:17,251">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">- [Tiffany] And development # 2 - the Internet</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:41:17,251" end="00:41:19,244">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">which started from the U.S. Defense Department</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:41:19,244" end="00:41:26,199">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">creating a decentralized system of defenseby linking together their computers.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:41:26,199" end="00:41:30,346">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Every step of progress has so many ripple effects.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:41:30,346" end="00:41:35,485">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">But no matter how much the world changes some things never change.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:41:35,485" end="00:41:37,891">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Like the only thing worsethan your parent</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:41:37,891" end="00:41:40,391">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">getting sick is your child getting sick.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:41:40,391" end="00:41:41,873">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">It was Halloween and our daughter, Odessa</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:41:41,873" end="00:41:46,104">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">got a severe pain in the right side of her stomach.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:41:46,104" end="00:41:48,087">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Ken called my father and described her symptoms.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:41:49,710" end="00:41:51,210">*My father said it was <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>appendicitis and that</p>
      <p begin="00:41:51,210" end="00:41:53,766">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">we needed to have her operated on immediately.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:41:53,766" end="00:41:56,755">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">If we didn't, her appendix will rupture.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:41:56,755" end="00:41:58,347">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">But at the hospital, the doctors wouldn't operate</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:41:58,347" end="00:42:00,696">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">unless they did a CAT scan.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:42:00,696" end="00:42:04,240">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">So we called my father againand he adamantly disagreed.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:42:04,240" end="00:42:07,874">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">He was worried about the impact of radiation on her long term health.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:42:07,874" end="00:42:12,075">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">He said don't let the doctors do this again.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:42:12,075" end="00:42:16,541">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">And then he went to go to sleepbecause he was so weak.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:42:16,541" end="00:42:18,938">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">At midnight she became much sicker and the doctor still refused</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:42:18,938" end="00:42:22,401">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">to operate without the scan.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:42:22,401" end="00:42:27,944">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">So Ken and I made the decision without my father.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:42:27,944" end="00:42:30,077">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">We approved the scan so that they'd operate on her</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:42:30,077" end="00:42:33,703">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">and when they did they discovered that her appendix had already ruptured.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:42:33,703" end="00:42:36,852">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">But we had caught it just in time.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:42:39,080" end="00:42:41,058">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">It was the first time my father wasn't able to see me</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:42:41,058" end="00:42:44,756">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">all the way through a major crisis.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:42:44,756" end="00:42:46,438">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">I realized that Ken and I were gonna have to make</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:42:46,438" end="00:42:50,318">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">a lot more of this big life decisions without him.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:42:51,965" end="00:42:56,239">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Everyone experiences that moment whenthey become the person who others turn to.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:42:58,547" end="00:43:01,143">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">It's like a big hand-off.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:43:01,611" end="00:43:06,768">$$ - And you are the person that they're <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>going to go to.</p>
      <p begin="00:43:09,167" end="00:43:11,043">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Was I ready?</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:43:12,499" end="00:43:18,815">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">There comes a time when we allhave to step into the next phase.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:43:18,815" end="00:43:22,156">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Every decision we make impacts everything around us,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:43:22,156" end="00:43:25,997">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">family community and the world.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:43:25,997" end="00:43:28,853">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">As we're becoming more connected, that impact is only becoming</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:43:28,853" end="00:43:31,942">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">stronger and faster.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:43:31,942" end="00:43:36,865">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">But with connections comes responsibility.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:43:36,865" end="00:43:39,318">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Are we as a specie ready to take that on?</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:43:45,841" end="00:43:49,876">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">- [Narrator] This left brain way of thinking became so successful</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:43:49,876" end="00:43:52,952">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">that humans felt they could create anything they wanted,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:43:52,952" end="00:43:58,339">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic"> whenever they wanted, without thinking of the cost.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:43:58,339" end="00:44:03,262">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">This insatiable desire to consume accelerated after World War II</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:44:03,262" end="00:44:07,174">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">when the American economy was flourishing.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:44:07,174" end="00:44:09,943">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">The men came home,the women had babies,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:44:09,943" end="00:44:15,690">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">and everyone started buying stuff.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:44:15,690" end="00:44:21,817">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">The idea was simple -- spend money and the economy would keep growing.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:44:21,817" end="00:44:25,918">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Which meant that production had to become hyper efficient.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:44:27,826" end="00:44:31,979">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Soon the world had become so connected, humans were able to divide up</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:44:31,979" end="00:44:34,049">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">different parts of production and outsourced those pieces</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:44:34,049" end="00:44:39,181">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic"> to places where production was cheapest.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:44:39,181" end="00:44:43,140">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">To some, this accelerated progress</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:44:45,819" end="00:44:49,822">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">and increased the standard of livingin developing countries.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:44:51,143" end="00:44:56,022">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">To others, it was colonialism with a remote control.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:44:58,562" end="00:45:03,362">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">To keep consumers consuming, products were made from plastic,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:45:03,362" end="00:45:10,421">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">so they would be disposed of quickly and people would have to buy more.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:45:12,052" end="00:45:20,307">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Today the average American consumes 195 lbs of stuff every single day.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:45:21,321" end="00:45:27,215">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">And worldwide, humans dig up theequivalent of 112 Empire State Buildings</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:45:27,215" end="00:45:31,668">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">worth of materials each day to make stuff.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:45:33,416" end="00:45:38,607">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">To a point where there is now a Texas-size island of plastic garbage</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:45:38,607" end="00:45:41,054">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">floating in the Pacific.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:45:41,389" end="00:45:46,722">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">It is believed to be the largest man-made structure in the world.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:45:47,309" end="00:45:50,363">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">A giant sign the says,"PAY ATTENTION"</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:45:50,363" end="00:45:53,338">[slap]</p>
      <p begin="00:45:53,338" end="00:45:57,015">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">like the bees.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:45:57,015" end="00:46:02,248">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Somewhere along the way humans started shipping them from farm to farm,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:46:02,248" end="00:46:05,617">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">seventy thousand of them at a time.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:46:05,617" end="00:46:08,575">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">And rather than feed them a variety of food,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:46:08,575" end="00:46:11,075">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">they isolated the one type of food,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:46:11,075" end="00:46:18,231">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">that was cheapest and most efficient to feed them, corn syrup.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:46:20,204" end="00:46:26,347">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">With everything the bees are up against, it's no wonder they're disappearing.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:46:28,086" end="00:46:31,830">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">So many of today's problems are the by-products of the human drive</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:46:31,830" end="00:46:34,688">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">for efficiency and growth.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:46:35,888" end="00:46:38,040">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Although people are multiplying,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:46:38,040" end="00:46:39,294">[flapping]</p>
      <p begin="00:46:40,960" end="00:46:43,310">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">resources are not.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:46:49,577" end="00:46:55,478">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Humans invented technology to survive amid scarcity.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:46:55,478" end="00:46:59,601">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Technology transforms nature into resources that appear</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:46:59,601" end="00:47:02,094">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">to be always available.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:47:02,675" end="00:47:05,015">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">But humans are starting to view themselves</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:47:05,015" end="00:47:09,813">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">as resources that are always available.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:47:09,813" end="00:47:16,340">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">What began as a way to improve life, is now threatening to consume it.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:47:19,877" end="00:47:25,645">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Since the consequences of human actions are faster and more global than ever</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:47:25,645" end="00:47:30,792">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">how can the human species use this connectedness to its advantage,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:47:30,792" end="00:47:36,286">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">and take the next leap in human evolution?</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:47:36,286" end="00:47:38,737">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">- [Tiffany] Maybe our first step is to stop and think more</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:47:38,737" end="00:47:42,157">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">about where we wanna be headed.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:47:44,895" end="00:47:49,436">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">We're caught in this giant ball of problems spun from our desire for growth.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:47:51,744" end="00:47:54,706">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">And growth for growth's sake...</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:47:57,830" end="00:47:59,370">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">is cancer.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:48:02,109" end="00:48:08,273">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Somewhere along the way, did we lose our sense of what's important?</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:48:18,864" end="00:48:20,876">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">- [Narrator] There's an old story about a tourist who sees</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:48:20,876" end="00:48:25,655">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">a fisherman resting and asked why he is not working.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:48:25,655" end="00:48:29,495">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">The fisherman said he already caught enough fish for the day.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:48:29,495" end="00:48:33,210">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">The tourist explained that if he caught more fish he could sell them</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:48:33,210" end="00:48:38,569">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">and use the money to buy another boat, and hire workers to fish for him.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:48:38,569" end="00:48:41,876">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">If he worked really hard, in a few years he'd have a whole fleet of boats</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:48:41,876" end="00:48:44,736">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">and crews to man them.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:48:44,736" end="00:48:47,738">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">"Then what?"</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:48:47,738" end="00:48:51,844">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">"Well, you wouldn't have to work so hard,you could rest during the day."</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:48:51,844" end="00:48:56,660">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">The fisherman replied, "That's what I'm doing now."</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:48:57,650" end="00:49:00,831">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">- [Tiffany] It was very clear how I needed to spend my time.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:49:00,831" end="00:49:02,925">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">- [Dr. Shlain] Hi baby,this is your father</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:49:02,925" end="00:49:04,925">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">and I want to talk to you.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:49:04,925" end="00:49:09,223">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">so give me a call...</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:49:09,223" end="00:49:11,968">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">- My quest to capture my father on film grew stronger.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:49:11,968" end="00:49:17,100">[Father and Daughter] &#9834; And when <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>I'm with him, I love him so much &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:49:17,100" end="00:49:21,852">&#9834; I love my Daddy, my Daddy loves me &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:49:21,852" end="00:49:24,484">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">&#9834; papam papam pam yeahh &#9834;</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:49:24,484" end="00:49:27,284">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">- [Tiffany] My father's treatment was going really well.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:49:27,284" end="00:49:29,242">- [Dr. Shlain] Life's good.<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>- <span tts:fontStyle="italic">[Tiffany] Life is good.</span></p>
      <p begin="00:49:29,242" end="00:49:30,935">- Life is good.</p>
      <p begin="00:49:30,935" end="00:49:33,923">[heart beat]<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/><span tts:fontStyle="italic">And then I got a call from my doctor.</span></p>
      <p begin="00:49:33,923" end="00:49:37,649">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">I was ready for bad news, but she said that the final pregnancy test</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:49:37,649" end="00:49:40,602">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">showed that the baby was gonna make it.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:49:40,602" end="00:49:45,066">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">All the miscarriages, years of trying, finally we're gonna have another baby,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:49:45,066" end="00:49:47,159">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">a sibling for our daughter.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:49:47,159" end="00:49:53,820">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">- We just found out.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:49:53,820" end="00:49:59,057">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Having a sibling for Odessa was so important to her and to me.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:49:59,057" end="00:50:00,871">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Going through infertility really made me question</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:50:00,871" end="00:50:03,707">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">why I wanted to have to have another child so badly.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:50:03,707" end="00:50:07,487">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Especially with all thepopulation issues in our world</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:50:07,487" end="00:50:11,607">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">which is connected to everything else.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:50:15,633" end="00:50:20,069">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">By 2050 we'll have close to nine billion people.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:50:20,069" end="00:50:23,037">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">How many people can our world take?</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:50:25,704" end="00:50:27,736">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">China focused on the over population issue</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:50:27,736" end="00:50:31,647">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">by instituting their one child rule policy.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:50:31,647" end="00:50:34,839">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">It had many unintended consequences.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:50:34,839" end="00:50:39,114">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Like a country with more men than women</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:50:39,114" end="00:50:40,549">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">or a whole generation of adults</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:50:40,549" end="00:50:46,344">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">with no brothers and sisters, no cousins, aunts or uncles.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:50:46,344" end="00:50:49,305">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">And now these only children are taking care of two parents,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:50:49,305" end="00:50:52,970">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">and sometimes four grandparentsby themselves.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:50:52,970" end="00:50:54,879">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">And now that people are living so much longer</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:50:54,879" end="00:50:59,395">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">it could be eight great grandparents, too.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:50:59,395" end="00:51:01,091">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">My brother, sister and I were really thankful</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:51:01,091" end="00:51:05,127">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">to have each other during this period.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:51:05,127" end="00:51:06,815">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">I definitely understood on a whole new level</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:51:06,815" end="00:51:10,067">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">the support siblings provide.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:51:11,646" end="00:51:15,895">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">When were kids our dad use to point to a clustered redwood trees and say,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:51:15,895" end="00:51:19,793">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">"Those look like individual trees, but they're all one tree."</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:51:19,793" end="00:51:24,751">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">"They have the same root structure, it's like a family."</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:51:24,751" end="00:51:30,289">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">This concept could apply to all living things.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:51:30,289" end="00:51:33,266">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">My Mom used to say, siblingsare the longest relationship</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:51:33,266" end="00:51:35,186">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">you'll have in your life.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:51:35,186" end="00:51:41,968">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">They know the good times, the bad, the neuroses, all that shared history.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:51:44,079" end="00:51:47,078">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">And specially now without being able to lean</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:51:47,078" end="00:51:51,350">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">on our father, we all turned to each other.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:51:52,935" end="00:51:58,137">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">My stepmother Aina, would let us know every morning how he was doing.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:51:58,137" end="00:52:02,153">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">And my sister Kimberly who's an artist, worked out her feelings on canvass.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:52:02,153" end="00:52:05,712">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">We would talk to each other everyday.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:52:05,712" end="00:52:07,018">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">My brother Jordan who is a doctor,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:52:07,018" end="00:52:13,106">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">interpreted all themedical reports for us.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:52:13,106" end="00:52:15,430">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Then one day, my brother calledto report that our father's</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:52:15,430" end="00:52:17,004">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">white blood cells were so low</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:52:17,004" end="00:52:21,357">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">that we should start preparing ourselves.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:52:22,820" end="00:52:26,623">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">The next day I went with my fatherto the hospital for treatment.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:52:26,623" end="00:52:29,835">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">And I was sitting next to him holding his hand and I said,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:52:29,835" end="00:52:33,771">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">I know we didn't get to collaborate the way we wanted to on this film.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:52:33,771" end="00:52:38,354">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">But I want you to know that I'm gonna dedicate the film to you.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:52:41,119" end="00:52:44,339">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Throughout all of this, Ken was really there for us.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:52:44,339" end="00:52:47,566">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">He had lost his own fatherto leukemia when he was twenty-one.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:52:47,566" end="00:52:50,301">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">So he understood what we were going through.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:52:50,301" end="00:52:54,240">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">We were both really present for each other.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:52:54,240" end="00:52:57,064">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">We started unplugging from our computers one day a week.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:52:57,064" end="00:53:00,436"><span tts:fontStyle="italic">We called it our technology</span> Shabbats.</p>
      <p begin="00:53:00,436" end="00:53:01,702">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">And meanwhile, no matter how sick he felt,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:53:01,702" end="00:53:03,302">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">my father was determined</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:53:03,302" end="00:53:06,078">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">to finish his book on Da Vinci.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:53:06,078" end="00:53:09,120">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">He kept saying,"I will live to meet your baby"</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:53:09,120" end="00:53:13,397">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">and "I'm going to finish the book.""</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:53:13,397" end="00:53:15,031">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">It was like my father was trying</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:53:15,031" end="00:53:17,231">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">to download his print before it was too late.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:53:17,231" end="00:53:21,073">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">He was so close, he was on that last chapter.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:53:21,073" end="00:53:22,708">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">And as he was writing, I was reading the latest draft</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:53:22,708" end="00:53:26,592">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">as fast as I could so we could talk about it.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:53:26,592" end="00:53:28,094">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">I knew he was getting at something big</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:53:28,094" end="00:53:30,894">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">about the direction where human species is headed.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:53:30,894" end="00:53:34,010">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">But I wasn't sure yet where he was gonna land.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:53:34,010" end="00:53:36,632">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">But ultimately I was just happy to see him focus on something</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:53:36,632" end="00:53:41,018">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">he was passionate about instead of thinking about his cancer.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:53:41,018" end="00:53:45,280">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">We organized lots of impromptu family gatherings and dinners.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:53:45,280" end="00:53:48,439">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">This whole crisis definitelyput our priorities in order.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:53:48,439" end="00:53:54,005">&#9834; [music] &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:53:54,005" end="00:53:56,252">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">- [Narrator] There had been moments throughout history when crisis</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:53:56,252" end="00:54:01,644">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">made people re-evaluatethe way they think about the world.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:54:04,404" end="00:54:06,749">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">In the 1960's groups all over the world</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:54:06,749" end="00:54:10,468">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">invested themselves in one another's struggles,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:54:10,468" end="00:54:13,967">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">because they realized the interdependence of human race.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:54:13,967" end="00:54:21,737">&#9834; [music] &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:54:21,737" end="00:54:27,257">- [JF Kennedy] ... to achieve economic <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>growth and social progress</p>
      <p begin="00:54:27,257" end="00:54:28,984">throughout the America.</p>
      <p begin="00:54:28,984" end="00:54:32,924">.- $$ Women young and old, <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>women black and white,</p>
      <p begin="00:54:32,924" end="00:54:37,333">$$ women grandmothers who called <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>for the original right to vote</p>
      <p begin="00:54:37,333" end="00:54:41,245">&#9834; [music] &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:54:41,245" end="00:54:44,492">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">- [Narrator] In 1963 Martin Luther King Jr.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:54:44,492" end="00:54:47,492">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">wrote a letter from the Birmingham Jail.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:54:47,492" end="00:54:53,736">- $$ Injustice anywhere is a threat <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>to justice everywhere.</p>
      <p begin="00:54:53,736" end="00:54:59,249">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">- [Narrator] This greater sense of interdependence began to catch on.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:54:59,249" end="00:55:03,587">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Academia was beginning to embrace interdependence with systems theory,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:55:03,587" end="00:55:08,293">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">which studies how separate disciplines are interlinked.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:55:08,293" end="00:55:12,781">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">And a British scientist named Richard Dawkins showed how ideas</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:55:12,781" end="00:55:16,097">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">are inter-dependent, building on other ideas.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:55:16,097" end="00:55:20,955">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">He coined he term "meme", because ideas</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:55:20,955" end="00:55:24,955">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">like genes can reproduce,mutate and evolve.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:55:24,955" end="00:55:29,890">[plane taking off]<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>&#9834; [music] &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:55:29,890" end="00:55:32,590">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Interdependent thinking also accelerated</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:55:32,590" end="00:55:35,157">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">due to the proliferation ofelectronic media</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:55:35,157" end="00:55:38,534">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">like television which allowed people to see what was happening</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:55:38,534" end="00:55:43,656">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">in other parts of the world.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:55:43,656" end="00:55:46,236">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Communication theorist Marshall McLuhan</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:55:46,236" end="00:55:47,733">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">talked about this major shift</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:55:47,733" end="00:55:51,145">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">in the way humans were receiving information</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:55:51,145" end="00:55:54,818">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">noting that the medium is more important than the message.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:55:54,818" end="00:55:59,269">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">He believed that this electronic inter-dependence</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:55:59,269" end="00:56:05,813">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">would allow people to interact in what he called, a global village.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:56:05,813" end="00:56:07,998">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">- [Woman] My father who was really influenced by McLuhan</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:56:07,998" end="00:56:10,251">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">referred to the proliferation of visual media</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:56:10,251" end="00:56:14,954">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic"> as the iconic revolution</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:56:14,954" end="00:56:17,324">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">which started in the '20s when photography and film appeared</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:56:17,324" end="00:56:22,633">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">but really flourished with television in the '50s and '60s.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:56:22,633" end="00:56:25,179">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">He believed that this started toreactivate the collective</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:56:25,179" end="00:56:26,746">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">right hemisphere.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:56:27,790" end="00:56:30,798">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">And that as more and more images circulated through new technologies,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:56:30,798" end="00:56:36,063">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">women would continue to take on stronger roles in society</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:56:36,063" end="00:56:40,424">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">which would eventually lead to a more egalitarian view of the world.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:56:42,132" end="00:56:45,637">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">- [Narrator]Leonard Shlain referred to two images that did more to convey</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:56:45,637" end="00:56:50,752">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">the connectedness of the world than any text could have.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:56:50,752" end="00:56:57,102">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">The first showed the result of thousands of years of left brain damage.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:56:57,102" end="00:57:01,566">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">And the second demonstrated the shift back to the right hemisphere,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:57:01,566" end="00:57:03,484">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">the big picture.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:57:04,531" end="00:57:07,261">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">This image sent to Earth from Apollo VIII</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:57:07,261" end="00:57:10,885">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">helped popularize the Gaia hypothesis,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:57:10,885" end="00:57:15,813">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">a new theory by NASA scientist named James Lovelock.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:57:15,813" end="00:57:20,870">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">The Gaia theory suggested that the planet was one single organism,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:57:20,870" end="00:57:26,551">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">an interdependent biological network that connects all life.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:57:27,993" end="00:57:32,443">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">All spiritual practices at their core show how individually,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:57:32,443" end="00:57:37,660">every person is a part of something <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>larger than themselves.</p>
      <p begin="00:57:37,660" end="00:57:42,902">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">A primal connection that many cultures understand as the basis of existence.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:57:42,902" end="00:57:46,137">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">And yet a lot of usseem to keep forgetting it,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:57:46,137" end="00:57:50,342">[bomb exploding]</p>
      <p begin="00:57:50,342" end="00:57:56,596">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">until moments of crisis or moments like seeing the Earth for the first time</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:57:56,596" end="00:58:03,693">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">when humans shift their perspective, see the bigger picture and re-prioritize.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:58:05,534" end="00:58:09,691">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">- [Woman] My father's own priorities also shifted in the early '70s.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:58:11,331" end="00:58:14,166">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">I remember I was four years old, running after him one day saying,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:58:14,166" end="00:58:17,378">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">"Daddy! Daddy! I see colors around people.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:58:17,378" end="00:58:20,551">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">He said, "You do?" and you know,this was Northern California in the '70s</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:58:20,551" end="00:58:24,459">and he was really interested <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>in the psychedelic of it all.</p>
      <p begin="00:58:24,459" end="00:58:28,121">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">- [Dr. Shlain] So I said, "Well, what color did you see in Jordan?</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:58:28,121" end="00:58:29,635">- [Woman] Green</p>
      <p begin="00:58:29,635" end="00:58:31,839">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">- [Dr. Shlain] I said, what about Kimberly?</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:58:31,839" end="00:58:33,012">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">- [Tiffany] Orange</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:58:33,012" end="00:58:35,501">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">- [Dr. Shlain] So I said, what -- what color did you see in Mother?</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:58:35,501" end="00:58:38,182">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">- [Tiffany] I said yellow.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:58:39,428" end="00:58:41,399">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">- [Dr. Shlain] What about me?</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:58:41,399" end="00:58:46,178">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">- [Tiffany] And he turned to me and I said, "Black, it's all around you."</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:58:47,455" end="00:58:49,960">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">And then about four months later, he was diagnosed with cancer</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:58:49,960" end="00:58:51,923">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">for the first time.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:58:51,923" end="00:58:56,963">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">He was 37 and he was toldthat he was gonna die.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:59:00,442" end="00:59:02,386">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">But he wanted to try and beat the odds and he started</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:59:02,386" end="00:59:05,297">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">this experimental radiation treatment.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:59:05,820" end="00:59:11,495">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">After that he used to ask me what color he was all the time.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:59:12,880" end="00:59:14,388">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">And one day he said, "What color am I?"</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:59:14,388" end="00:59:17,463">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">and I had just gotten a new set of Crayola markers,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:59:17,463" end="00:59:20,535">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">and I saw magenta all around him.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:59:20,865" end="00:59:25,831">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">And then shortly thereafter, he went into a miraculous remission.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:59:25,831" end="00:59:31,177">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">He had always felt that he had beengiven a second lease on life.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:59:31,177" end="00:59:35,558">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">- [Dr. Shlain] So I decided that I would,absolutely</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:59:35,558" end="00:59:38,368">become dedicated to my children.</p>
      <p begin="00:59:38,368" end="00:59:47,407">[kids singing]</p>
      <p begin="00:59:47,407" end="00:59:52,387">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">- Here I was wanting to see magenta again.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:59:52,387" end="00:59:58,168">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">It is January 30th, 2009 and, uhhh--</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:59:58,168" end="00:59:59,398">- Here I am [laughs].</p>
      <p begin="00:59:59,398" end="01:00:01,233">- [Tifanny] <span tts:fontStyle="italic">You're here.</span></p>
      <p begin="01:00:01,233" end="01:00:03,590">- Yes, I'm still here, [laughs]..</p>
      <p begin="01:00:03,590" end="01:00:04,634">[Tiffany] <span tts:fontStyle="italic">That's a bright gift--</span></p>
      <p begin="01:00:04,634" end="01:00:05,870">- Um well, I mean, uh --</p>
      <p begin="01:00:05,870" end="01:00:07,361">[Tiffany] <span tts:fontStyle="italic">That's just that.</span></p>
      <p begin="01:00:07,361" end="01:00:10,148">- I had doubts six months ago.</p>
      <p begin="01:00:10,148" end="01:00:14,706">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">- My father was again offered to do an experimental treatment.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:00:14,706" end="01:00:21,304">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">And just like when he was 37, he wanted to try to beat the odds.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:00:21,304" end="01:00:25,162">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">And then the crazy thing is, it did work.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:00:25,162" end="01:00:29,542">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">The new treatment shrunk his tumor by 70%. We were stunned.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:00:29,542" end="01:00:32,067">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Everyone was stunned.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:00:36,252" end="01:00:39,937">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">The brain is an amazing resilient thing.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:00:43,459" end="01:00:47,705">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">I'd always shared my father's interest in the brain.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:00:47,705" end="01:00:50,979">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">When I was 22, I tried to make a film called "Zoli's Brain"</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:00:50,979" end="01:00:54,655">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">That took place entirely inside of the sculptor's mind.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:00:54,655" end="01:00:57,221">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">There were characters that represented different functions of the brain</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:00:57,221" end="01:00:59,801">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">like the ID and the ego,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:00:59,801" end="01:01:02,190">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">and editors that decided what thoughts get spoken</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:01:02,190" end="01:01:05,923">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">and which ones get locked away.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:01:05,923" end="01:01:08,873">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Zoli's Brain was my first big failure.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:01:08,873" end="01:01:13,428">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">It's still sitting unedited in boxes in my garage.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:01:13,428" end="01:01:15,325">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Someday I wanna finish it.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:01:15,325" end="01:01:20,096">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">But that was 20 years ago, today would be such a different film.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:01:20,096" end="01:01:24,645">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">We' ve learned so much more about how the brain works.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:01:24,645" end="01:01:26,526">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">And we're also creating new tools that are changing</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:01:26,526" end="01:01:30,296">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">the way we process information.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:01:30,296" end="01:01:32,735">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">So how was our ever increasing connectedness</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:01:32,735" end="01:01:36,280">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">changing the ways our brains function?</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:01:36,280" end="01:01:38,190">[popping sound]</p>
      <p begin="01:01:40,886" end="01:01:43,274">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">- [Narrator] The human brain is one of the most complex</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:01:43,274" end="01:01:45,722">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">biological systems on earth,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:01:45,722" end="01:01:52,913">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">consisting of a hundred billions neurons,processing 70,000 thoughts a day,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:01:53,481" end="01:01:59,057">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">that releases a hormone called oxytocin when humans connect with each other.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:02:01,435" end="01:02:08,474">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Their brains also release oxytocin whenthey hug for more than six seconds.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:02:08,474" end="01:02:11,070">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">New mothers are flooded with it.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:02:13,238" end="01:02:17,463">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Oxytocin decreases fear and anxiety</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:02:17,463" end="01:02:22,463">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">and creates empathy, trust and cooperation,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:02:22,463" end="01:02:26,515">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">which re-enforces our urge to connect.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:02:26,515" end="01:02:29,138">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">But sometimes we overdo it.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:02:29,138" end="01:02:32,468">[beeping]</p>
      <p begin="01:02:32,468" end="01:02:38,366">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Some studies show that multitasking drops I.Q. scores by ten points,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:02:38,366" end="01:02:43,713">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">It's the equivalent of being stoned.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:02:43,713" end="01:02:47,361">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">The human brain is also designedto seek pleasure,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:02:47,361" end="01:02:51,627">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">because of a hormone called dopamine</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:02:51,972" end="01:02:58,835">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">which trains human to do things that make them feel good over and over again.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:02:58,835" end="01:03:01,825">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Researchers now know that the brain releases dopamine</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:03:01,825" end="01:03:04,668">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">when a new information is received.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:03:04,668" end="01:03:10,049">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">So every click, search, tweet or text has the potential to stimulate.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:03:10,049" end="01:03:15,433">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">the same hormonal rush as sex, drugs and rock and roll.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:03:15,433" end="01:03:19,230">[screaming]</p>
      <p begin="01:03:19,230" end="01:03:22,205">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">But an interesting happens with dopamine.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:03:22,205" end="01:03:24,579">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">You never fully feel satiated.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:03:24,584" end="01:03:29,420">It's called an infinite dopamine loop,<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>when humans fall</p>
      <p begin="01:03:29,420" end="01:03:33,776">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">into an infinite cycle of wanting more.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:03:33,776" end="01:03:40,364">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Which might explain human's insatiable hunger for knowledge and connection.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:03:42,500" end="01:03:46,371">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">- [Tiffany] It could also explain my sneaking off to tweet.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:03:46,371" end="01:03:52,670">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Sophocles once said, "Nothing vast entersthe life of mortals without a curse."</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:03:53,587" end="01:03:58,307">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">My father always used this in his books and I think about it all the time</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:03:58,307" end="01:04:02,431">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Technology is vast and has so much potential.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:04:02,431" end="01:04:04,402">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">But it's also a curse.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:04:04,402" end="01:04:07,911">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Our attention is pulled in so many different directions.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:04:07,911" end="01:04:13,656">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">But connecting wildly can sometimes be at the cost of connecting deeply.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:04:14,314" end="01:04:19,631">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">The important thing becomes to prioritizehow we focus our attention.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:04:19,631" end="01:04:25,115">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Knowing how to plug in mindfully and also knowing when to unplug.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:04:25,115" end="01:04:27,458">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Because we can't escape these technologies</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:04:27,458" end="01:04:32,008">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">we're only gonna become morereliant on them.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:04:32,008" end="01:04:34,559">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">In one of my father's books, he points</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:04:34,559" end="01:04:36,559">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">to the theory that computers and technology</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:04:36,559" end="01:04:38,685">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">are extensions of our brain.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:04:40,405" end="01:04:44,080">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">He writes that the human brainhad to stop growing at a certain point</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:04:44,080" end="01:04:48,418">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">because its large size was causing women to die during childbirth.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:04:48,418" end="01:04:51,910">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">And if the brain had continued to grow,too many women would die</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:04:51,910" end="01:04:54,690">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">and so would the human species.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:04:54,690" end="01:04:57,293">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Which is why we eventually createdtechnologies</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:04:57,293" end="01:04:59,525">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">to extend our brain's capabilities</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:05:00,627" end="01:05:08,276">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Extended brains, first on our desks then on our pockets and now on the clouds.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:05:08,276" end="01:05:11,694">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">A brain with infinite possiblities.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:05:12,864" end="01:05:14,486">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">My father's new book about Da Vinci</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:05:14,486" end="01:05:17,186">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">built on ideasfrom all of his other books.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:05:17,186" end="01:05:20,078">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">He kept saying the he was so excited for me</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:05:20,078" end="01:05:23,078">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">to read that last chapter when it was done.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:05:23,078" end="01:05:28,649">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">And I'll never forget when he called and announced, "I've finished the book."</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:05:28,649" end="01:05:31,933">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Although I had a hard time understanding what this new book was about,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:05:31,933" end="01:05:37,288">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">when I read that last draft, it all became clear.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:05:37,288" end="01:05:42,177">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">My father was saying that in every speciean occasional genetic mutation occurs,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:05:42,177" end="01:05:48,440">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">that offers a unique glimpse into where the species could be headed.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:05:48,440" end="01:05:51,455">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">He believed Da Vinci offered thatglimpse showing us</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:05:51,455" end="01:05:54,621">what a human being <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>could achieve if they could synthesize</p>
      <p begin="01:05:54,621" end="01:05:58,856">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">both the left and the right hemispheres of the brain.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:05:58,856" end="01:06:01,142">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">I love this idea.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:06:01,142" end="01:06:03,804">[cheering]</p>
      <p begin="01:06:03,804" end="01:06:04,990">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">All of a sudden the answer of how</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:06:04,990" end="01:06:06,803">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">we can use our increasing connectedness</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:06:06,803" end="01:06:12,220">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">to tackle the problems we face seemed clear.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:06:12,220" end="01:06:15,033">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Five hundred years after Da Vinci, we're seeing a new glimpse</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:06:15,033" end="01:06:19,133">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">into the future of our species.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:06:19,133" end="01:06:21,767">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Still in its infancy the Internet is helping each of us</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:06:21,767" end="01:06:24,953">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">to synthesize the two hemispheres of our mind.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:06:24,953" end="01:06:30,234">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Clicking to the radical explosion of text information</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:06:30,234" end="01:06:31,768">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">online is activating the left hemisphere.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:06:31,768" end="01:06:33,302">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">And linking from page to page, viideo to video,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:06:33,302" end="01:06:36,779">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">is stimulating the right hemisphere.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:06:36,779" end="01:06:39,381">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">The Internet is literally changing the way we think.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:06:39,381" end="01:06:42,768">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Moving us through a constantly evolving landscape of words and images </span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:06:42,768" end="01:06:48,346">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">at a touch of a key stroke, synthesizing the two hemispheres of our brain.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:06:48,346" end="01:06:51,329"><span tts:fontStyle="italic">If this re-wiring of the brain</span><br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>is happening on an individual level*</p>
      <p begin="01:06:51,329" end="01:06:53,883">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">to each person who uses the web,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:06:53,883" end="01:06:57,106">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">imagine the cumulative effect of a Da Vinci type brain</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:06:57,106" end="01:07:00,132">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">synthesis on a global scale.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:07:00,132" end="01:07:06,058">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Today there are close to two billion people online.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:07:06,058" end="01:07:12,308">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">What would the world look like if everyoneon the planet could be online?</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:07:12,308" end="01:07:14,712">*It's not that far away.</p>
      <p begin="01:07:14,712" end="01:07:19,332">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">There are already five billion cellphones on the planet</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:07:19,332" end="01:07:22,177">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">We're at the beginning of a participatory revolution,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:07:35,393" end="01:07:48,609">&#9834; [music] &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="01:07:48,609" end="01:07:50,195">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">where people's ideas are free to interact, </span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:07:50,195" end="01:07:57,421">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">reproduce and cross pollinateinstantaneously,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:07:57,421" end="01:08:00,693">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">creating new hybrid ideas that combine perspectives from all over the world,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:08:00,693" end="01:08:04,377">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">connecting ideas, data and cultures from millions of brains into</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:08:04,377" end="01:08:08,670">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">a global thinking structure with infinite possiblities.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:08:09,573" end="01:08:09,574">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">firing out to everyone you're connected to.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:08:09,574" end="01:08:12,453">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Rich text, hyperlink or tweet is like a neural synapse</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:08:12,453" end="01:08:16,524">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">firing out to everyone you're connected to.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:08:19,085" end="01:08:24,362">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">And with each connection you get a surge of oxytocin.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:08:24,362" end="01:08:30,395">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">It's like the Internet is creating a global network for oxytocin to flow.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:08:32,212" end="01:08:36,214">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Which makes us more empatheticinclined to share and collaborate,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:08:36,214" end="01:08:40,203">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">and driven to connect even more.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:08:40,203" end="01:08:45,716">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">The Internet is re-wiring our brains to think interdependently.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:08:47,443" end="01:08:52,644">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Changing the way we connect to the world online and off.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:08:56,089" end="01:08:58,017">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">I thought about what my mother said,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:08:58,017" end="01:09:03,027">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">that emotional connection drives everything we do.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:09:05,149" end="01:09:09,254">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">So if we can just channel that emotional connection,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:09:09,254" end="01:09:11,667">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">we'll be compelled to work together to solve the problems we face</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:09:11,667" end="01:09:15,462">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">and take humanity to the next level.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:09:15,462" end="01:09:17,678">[splash]</p>
      <p begin="01:09:20,752" end="01:09:24,331">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">This, combined with all the other ways to connect and make change,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:09:24,331" end="01:09:28,733">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">are gonna take us to a whole new place.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:09:28,733" end="01:09:32,131">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">As we become more connected we'll be able to see the cause and effect</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:09:32,131" end="01:09:40,006">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">of our actions in real time --what we buy, donate even throw away.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:09:40,006" end="01:09:42,455">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">We're just starting to unlock and share information</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:09:42,455" end="01:09:46,484">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">about the hundred trillion things that we've made in this world.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:09:46,484" end="01:09:50,017">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Once we understand this supply chain and see the links of our actions,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:09:50,017" end="01:09:56,083">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">it's gonna make us more thoughtful and conscious about our behavior.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:09:56,083" end="01:10:00,408">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Imagine if everyone was thinking interdependently,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:10:00,408" end="01:10:04,820">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">the ripple effect would change the world.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:10:04,820" end="01:10:08,205">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">If we can just be conscious of the curse.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:10:08,214" end="01:10:14,709">&#9834; [music] &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="01:10:14,709" end="01:10:17,215">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">- [Narrator] In the beginning,the invention of the alphabet</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:10:17,215" end="01:10:22,921">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">rewired the human brain to divide everything into isolated parts</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:10:22,921" end="01:10:27,308">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">which helped human beings to understand the world better.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:10:27,308" end="01:10:35,678">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">This approach led to great progress which eventually accelerated</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:10:35,678" end="01:10:38,189">until it threatened to consume.*</p>
      <p begin="01:10:38,189" end="01:10:40,700">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Today the human species is at a crossroads.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:10:40,700" end="01:10:47,448">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">There are more humans on the planet than ever before,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:10:47,448" end="01:10:52,164">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">and they are more connectedthan ever before.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:10:52,164" end="01:10:56,405">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">If we can harness the potential of all our minds</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:10:56,405" end="01:10:59,707">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">we can beat the odds.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:10:59,707" end="01:11:03,202">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">We have to.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:11:03,202" end="01:11:08,469">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">The world is only going to become more and more interdependent.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:11:08,469" end="01:11:14,991">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Like a beehive, every bee contributesto the survival of its colony.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:11:14,991" end="01:11:23,201">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">No bee can survive on its own.No human can survive on its own either.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:11:23,201" end="01:11:28,372">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Our survival depends on us connecting to one another.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:11:28,372" end="01:11:31,219">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">But connecting broadly is meaningless</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:11:31,219" end="01:11:36,799">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">unless we connect deeply.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:11:36,799" end="01:11:39,102">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">- [Tiffany] Two weeks before my due date things took a turn</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:11:39,102" end="01:11:41,868">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">for the worse with my father.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:11:41,868" end="01:11:44,277">The treatment stopped working.</p>
      <p begin="01:11:44,277" end="01:11:48,736">And I remember Aina called and said, <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>"He couldn't get out of bed."</p>
      <p begin="01:11:48,736" end="01:11:50,780">"But he wanted us all to come over</p>
      <p begin="01:11:50,780" end="01:11:54,479">'cause he had something<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>really important to tell us."</p>
      <p begin="01:11:54,479" end="01:11:56,815">And I'll never forget it, <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>it was this beautiful day,</p>
      <p begin="01:11:56,815" end="01:11:58,701">all the windows were open.</p>
      <p begin="01:11:58,701" end="01:12:03,707">And we're all gathered around him, <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>and my father leaned forward and said,</p>
      <p begin="01:12:03,707" end="01:12:05,547">"I had a realization."</p>
      <p begin="01:12:05,558" end="01:12:09,398">And we all leaned and so ready<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>to hear what he had to say,</p>
      <p begin="01:12:09,774" end="01:12:12,731">and it was that exact moment <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>that he lost his ability</p>
      <p begin="01:12:12,731" end="01:12:15,441">to speak for good.</p>
      <p begin="01:12:15,441" end="01:12:20,798">And as he lay there unable to speak, <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>we each got time alone with him.</p>
      <p begin="01:12:20,798" end="01:12:24,054">And I remember holding <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>his hand saying,</p>
      <p begin="01:12:24,054" end="01:12:29,434">"Daddy you can let go, I'm gonna be okay."</p>
      <p begin="01:12:29,434" end="01:12:32,042">"Thank you so much for everything <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>that you've taught me."</p>
      <p begin="01:12:32,042" end="01:13:47,455">&#9834; [music] &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="01:13:49,316" end="01:13:58,953">[people bustling]</p>
      <p begin="01:13:58,953" end="01:14:01,668">On Monday morning, when Ania called<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>to say he passed away,</p>
      <p begin="01:14:01,668" end="01:14:08,116">my first instinct was to call him<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>and tell him the news...</p>
      <p begin="01:14:13,269" end="01:14:16,137">About two months ago, I mustered<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>the courage to ask him</p>
      <p begin="01:14:16,137" end="01:14:20,588">what he wanted his funeral to be like.</p>
      <p begin="01:14:20,588" end="01:14:24,349">And surprisingly he said,<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>he only wanted to be here.</p>
      <p begin="01:14:24,349" end="01:14:27,488">[Laughter]</p>
      <p begin="01:14:27,488" end="01:14:32,427">But knowing my Dad, <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>he didn't really surprise me.</p>
      <p begin="01:14:32,427" end="01:14:35,642">And then he said, he had an idea<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>and he asked for my help.</p>
      <p begin="01:14:35,642" end="01:14:37,331">Here it is.</p>
      <p begin="01:14:43,317" end="01:14:44,423">- [Dr. Shlain ] <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Oh hi everybody!- -</span></p>
      <p begin="01:14:44,423" end="01:14:46,176">[audience laughing]</p>
      <p begin="01:14:46,176" end="01:14:51,031">My daughter told me to attend <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>my funeral so, I'm here.</p>
      <p begin="01:14:51,031" end="01:14:53,765">But I'm really not here.<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>I'm somewhere else but I can't tell you.</p>
      <p begin="01:14:53,765" end="01:14:57,983">It's a secret, uhm, nobody knows.</p>
      <p begin="01:14:58,075" end="01:15:02,584">I love you all <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>and I'm really gonna miss you.</p>
      <p begin="01:15:02,584" end="01:15:11,172">And the truth is, I'll always be with you.</p>
      <p begin="01:15:20,865" end="01:15:58,505">&#9834; [music] &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="01:15:58,505" end="01:16:02,799">- And while I was so worried <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>what the world would be like without him,</p>
      <p begin="01:16:02,799" end="01:16:07,772">I understand that everything he taught me <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>is still guiding me right now,</p>
      <p begin="01:16:07,772" end="01:16:12,554">right here as I'm talking to you, <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>even though I was a li'l nervous to do it.</p>
      <p begin="01:16:12,554" end="01:16:15,716">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">I realized that my father and I, like our species in our planet,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:16:15,716" end="01:16:21,252">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">our past and our future,are fundamentally interdependent.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:16:21,252" end="01:16:24,462">The Talmud has this saying that, <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>when you teach your children,</p>
      <p begin="01:16:24,462" end="01:16:27,038">you teach your children's children.</p>
      <p begin="01:16:27,038" end="01:16:29,866">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">We're standing here on the edge of all human knowledge</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:16:29,866" end="01:16:32,445">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">ready to take that lead.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:16:32,445" end="01:16:33,949">We've got to push on that edge <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>and you know,</p>
      <p begin="01:16:33,949" end="01:16:35,958">my father used to always say,</p>
      <p begin="01:16:35,958" end="01:16:41,858">If you're not living on the edge,<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>you're taking up way too much space.</p>
      <p begin="01:16:41,858" end="01:16:45,385">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">So here we are on the verge of taking that lead.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:16:45,385" end="01:16:48,158">For centuries,<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>we've been declaring independence</p>
      <p begin="01:16:48,158" end="01:16:51,912">and perhaps it's time to finally<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>declare our interdependence.</p>
      <p begin="01:16:51,912" end="24:00:00,000">&#9834; [music] &#9834;</p>
    </div>
